  ('disabled-23e15ae5-moex-00364', 'disabled-23e15ae5', 'disabled-23e15ae5-moex-110-f162a9a1', 'sub-disabled-23e15ae5-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有兩個數字X = 3D 和Y = D1 ，這兩個數字經過AND邏輯運算，將結', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "502793343f5f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2cc2181c2863", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "503", "s": "1317", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電腦打字"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-23e15ae5-moex-00365', 'disabled-23e15ae5', 'disabled-23e15ae5-moex-110-f162a9a1', 'sub-disabled-23e15ae5-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '16 果存入Z，請問Z的內容以十六進位表示時，結果為何？', '["10", "11", "12", "EE"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "502793343f5f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2cc2181c2863", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "503", "s": "1317", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電腦打字"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-23e15ae5-moex-00366', 'disabled-23e15ae5', 'disabled-23e15ae5-moex-110-f162a9a1', 'sub-disabled-23e15ae5-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於二元搜索（binarysearch）的演算法描述，何者錯誤？', '["二元搜索的演算法是假設要被搜索的陣列中項目已排序好", "每一次的比較後，可以減少一半的陣列不用去尋找", "二元搜索的演算法是陣列的中間處開始", "二元搜索在第一次的比較後，將陣列切為兩半，隨機選取任意一半繼續 尋找"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "502793343f5f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2cc2181c2863", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "503", "s": "1317", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電腦打字"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-23e15ae5-moex-00367', 'disabled-23e15ae5', 'disabled-23e15ae5-moex-110-f162a9a1', 'sub-disabled-23e15ae5-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據C語言的語法，若在宣告一個變數時前面加上下列那一種符號，則該 變數就是指標變數？', '["%", "/", "*", "#"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "502793343f5f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2cc2181c2863", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "503", "s": "1317", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電腦打字"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-23e15ae5-moex-00368', 'disabled-23e15ae5', 'disabled-23e15ae5-moex-110-f162a9a1', 'sub-disabled-23e15ae5-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '電腦運行中，可能會有中斷（interrupt）訊號發生，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["CPU 的動作是先將目前機械碼指令處理完，再處理中斷訊號，而非立 即處理此中斷訊號", "CPU 在處理中斷訊號時，一定要先關閉中斷機制，等到此中斷處理完 成，才能再開放中斷機制，否則期間又有中斷發生時，系統必然會出錯", "中斷訊號可能來自硬體電路，也可能來自軟體程式", "有些中斷訊號的發生時間可以預期"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "502793343f5f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2cc2181c2863", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "503", "s": "1317", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電腦打字"}'::jsonb, NULL),
